Yes, but I don't have to.

259
00:18:40,286 --> 00:18:44,499
No, it's okay.

260
00:18:46,292 --> 00:18:50,964
You know why?
Because you came to me first.

261
00:18:51,881 --> 00:18:55,802
I thought that would be
the best thing to do.

262
00:18:56,052 --> 00:18:58,805
You might have your work
cut out for you.

263
00:18:59,055 --> 00:19:04,894
When I talked to her, I got
the feeling she's into some other guy.

264
00:19:05,145 --> 00:19:09,899
See, that's actually what
I wanted to talk to you about.

265
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:12,944
I think I know who the other guy is.

266
00:19:13,194 --> 00:19:15,989
Who?

267
00:19:16,197 --> 00:19:17,615
It's me.

268
00:19:17,866 --> 00:19:20,035
I'm the other guy.

269
00:19:20,285 --> 00:19:22,495
What?

270
00:19:22,746 --> 00:19:27,334
When you were late last night,
Kathy and I got to talking...

271
00:19:27,584 --> 00:19:30,295
...and one thing led
to another, and...

272
00:19:30,545 --> 00:19:32,922
And what?
Did you sleep with her?

273
00:19:33,173 --> 00:19:34,758
No, I just kissed her.

274
00:19:35,008 --> 00:19:37,802
What? That's even worse!

275
00:19:38,053 --> 00:19:41,681
- How is that worse?
- It's the same!

276
00:19:41,931 --> 00:19:45,310
There's nothing I could do.
I'm in love with her!

277
00:19:45,560 --> 00:19:46,561
Who cares?

278
00:19:46,811 --> 00:19:49,856
You went behind my back?
I'd never do that to you!

279
00:19:50,106 --> 00:19:53,360
I have no excuses.
I was totally over the line.

280
00:19:53,610 --> 00:19:58,448
You're so far past the line,
that you can't even see the line!

281
00:19:58,698 --> 00:20:01,743
It's a dot to you!

282
00:20:02,077 --> 00:20:06,247
Yes, right! And I feel horrible.
You have to believe me.

283
00:20:06,498 --> 00:20:10,377
Is that why you bought all this?

284
00:20:10,627 --> 00:20:11,836
You know what?

285
00:20:12,087 --> 00:20:14,506
I will not watch your TV.

286
00:20:14,756 --> 00:20:16,549
I won't listen to your stereo.

287
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:21,054
And there's a loaf in the new
breadmaker I won't eat. Know why?

288
00:20:21,304 --> 00:20:22,222
Because...

289
00:20:22,472 --> 00:20:26,559
It's all tainted with your betrayal!

290
00:20:26,601 --> 00:20:33,024
This apartment is empty to me!
I'm not happy about you, either.

291
00:20:37,862 --> 00:20:40,156
And just so you know...

292
00:20:40,407 --> 00:20:44,202
...I made that bread for you.

293
00:20:57,340 --> 00:21:01,678
Oh, my God!
He's totally lost it.

294
00:21:04,639 --> 00:21:06,891
This cannot get any worse.

295
00:21:07,142 --> 00:21:11,730
Rats in the basement
are hanging themselves.

296
00:21:19,654 --> 00:21:23,408
Thank you. Thanks.

297
00:21:25,577 --> 00:21:28,455
I lost it.

298
00:21:29,122 --> 00:21:30,498
I won't play anymore.

299
00:21:30,749 --> 00:21:34,419
Would you...
Can you finish my set?

300
00:21:34,669 --> 00:21:37,672
After that? Yeah.

301
00:21:38,423 --> 00:21:42,177
No, I mean, if I can help.

302
00:21:46,264 --> 00:21:50,185
Like I could lose it.

303
00:21:51,561 --> 00:21:55,815
I played bad on purpose, guys.

304
00:21:56,691 --> 00:21:58,902
You were playing bad
this whole time.

305
00:21:59,152 --> 00:22:02,155
Just that last song.
